liboauth2
------------------------------------------
Generic library to build C-based OAuth 2.x and OpenID Connect servers and
clients e.g. web-server plugins.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.3-1
  libcjose-devel-0.6.2.3-1bl1
  libcjose0-0.6.2.3-1bl1
  libcurl-devel-8.14.1-1
  libcurl4-8.14.1-1
  libhiredis-devel-1.3.0-1bl1
  libhiredis1-1.3.0-1bl1
  libjansson-devel-2.13.1-1
  libjansson4-2.13.1-1
  libmemcached-devel-1.1.4-1bl1
  libmemcached11-1.1.4-1bl1
  liboauth2-devel-2.1.0-1bl2
  liboauth2_0-2.1.0-1bl2
  libpcre2-devel-10.45-1
  libpcre2_8_0-10.45-1
  libssl-devel-3.0.16-1
  libssl3-3.0.16-1
  pkg-config-2.4.3-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-2
  autoconf-archive-2024.10.16-1
  automake-20250528-1
  binutils-2.44-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  libcjose-devel-0.6.2.3-1bl1
  libcurl-devel-8.14.1-1
  libhiredis-devel-1.3.0-1bl1
  libjansson-devel-2.13.1-1
  libmemcached-devel-1.1.4-1bl1
  libpcre2-devel-10.45-1
  libssl-devel-3.0.16-1
  libtool-2.5.4-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/OpenIDC/liboauth2

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/OpenIDC/liboauth2/archive/refs/tags/v2.1.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack liboauth2-2.1.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./liboauth2-2.1.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/liboauth2-2.1.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liboauth2-2.1.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liboauth2_0-2.1.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liboauth2-devel-2.1.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(liboauth2)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/liboauth2.README
  /usr/share/doc/liboauth2/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/liboauth2/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/liboauth2/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/liboauth2/README.md

(liboauth2_0)
  /usr/bin/cygoauth2-0.dll

(liboauth2-devel)
  /usr/include/oauth2/cache.h
  /usr/include/oauth2/cfg.h
  /usr/include/oauth2/http.h
  /usr/include/oauth2/ipc.h
  /usr/include/oauth2/jose.h
  /usr/include/oauth2/log.h
  /usr/include/oauth2/mem.h
  /usr/include/oauth2/oauth2.h
  /usr/include/oauth2/openidc.h
  /usr/include/oauth2/proto.h
  /usr/include/oauth2/session.h
  /usr/include/oauth2/util.h
  /usr/include/oauth2/version.h
  /usr/lib/liboauth2.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/liboauth2.pc

